<br>
I have been grouping quite a bit since PoP in PoD killing the various spiders.  The Terrannis (spelling?) flavor was always annoying since most of them got off at least 1 complete heal no matter who was in the group.  A lot of groupmates have reported them unstunnable.  Well, since I first memmed the 61 pet, I have yet to see one get off a complete heal, not a single one.<br>
<br>
However, the most amusing incident was in Akheva last night playing around.  The Patrollers used to be nastly little casters and could drop a pet's hps quickly with a few spells.  Well, I was letting the 61 pet kill them for amusement and it was quite fun.  Out of about 10 of them before I got bored, the best one actually got my pet down to 96%, most of them didn't move him off of 100%.  That was with 0 heals and just pulling with a Malaise and throwing in one random nuke for xp.  They kept trying to cast and never got a spell off.  With spell effects on it was a riot.  They just stood there with flame coming out of their hands from spells in the process of being casted for a while then dropped over dead. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=103898" target="top">Baron Evelle Fyrestrike</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
